### 全局变量
@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api
@contentType = application/json
@username = testuser001
@password = password123
@email = test001@example.com

# 登录请求用于获取 Token
### 2. 用户登录
# @name login
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "username": "{{username}}",
    "password": "{{password}}"
}

### 11-2a. 获取公共歌单详情 (无需登录，验证 is_public)
GET {{baseUrl}}/song/playlist/public/1?page=1&limit=90

### 11-2b. 获取私有歌单详情 (需要登录，验证 owner_id)
GET {{baseUrl}}/song/playlist/private/1?page=1&limit=90
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}

### 14. 获取所有公开歌单 (无需登录)
GET {{baseUrl}}/song/playlists/public
# 返回 is_public=true 的歌单

### 14-2. 获取我的公开歌单 (需要登录)
GET {{baseUrl}}/song/playlists/user/public
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
# 返回 owner_id 为当前用户，且 is_public=true 的歌单

### 14-3. 获取我的私有歌单 (需要登录)
GET {{baseUrl}}/song/playlists/user/private
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
# 返回 owner_id 为当前用户，且 is_public=false 的歌单

### 15. 更新歌单信息(包括权限) (需要登录)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/song/playlist/1
Authorization: Bearer {{login.response.body.data.token}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
    "title": "已修改的歌单名称",
    "description": "这是新的描述",
    "is_public": false
}
